    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet this life though it frees, is not meant for mere victory."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God is full of intent and never could flow aimlessly."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So this life has a totality, a consummate issue encompassing me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life moves and life grows, life shapes as it flows"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now I share in this life’s destiny."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, I’ve got rivers of life flowing out of my innermost being!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’ve got rivers of life flowing out of my innermost being!"
            }
